subject: Lacrosse
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Northwestern has won the last three N.C.A.A. titles. The Wildcats (20-1) are seeded No. 1 here (Penn is No. 2). Northwestern’s offense is frenetic, its defense relentless in double teaming.
